&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">fragile
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">adj.   易損壞的；易碎的；脆弱的
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
